    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Nazi-- how should I say [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's a, it's the ones who belong to the, to the Hitler-- Party.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Party, there you go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[GERMAN] is party.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's so close.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] So they told me you cannot come into me anymore.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that was little by little, the thing started to go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I can remember that there was a paper, a newspaper, it's called And it was published from one of the biggest Nazis in the government.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it showed the real ugly side of Jewish people, with noses overdrawn.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And what they did, killing our children or, or cheating on this and that, that they are bad.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And if they are gone, then for us, the, the, the living will be so much better.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there's one thing, that every time when they're marched-- and there was some kind of a festival with them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So they marched, and around, around the homes, around the street.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then when they came to our home, they stopped.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then they start singing [GERMAN]-- no-- [GERMAN] What meant, [GERMAN], it's like this also.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I forgot about that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "When the knife, when the knife, from the Jewish blood runs off the knife, then things for us will go twice as good.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
